<h3 id="distance">Distance</h3>

<p>Stardex is the distance light travels in an Adex<br />
Setch = inch equivalent<br />
Setta = 20 setch<br />
Lirhetta = 40 setch (~1 meter, 1 meter = ~39.4 setch)<br />
Tekudex = 100,000 setch (~a mile and a half) or 5000 setta<br />
Hatadex = 10,000 Tekudex<br />
Metradex = 1,000,000 Tekudex</p>

<p>Nama-setch = 10th of a setch<br />
Seggeta = 100th of a setch<br />
Nama-seggata = 1000th of a setch<br /></p>

<p>cabre: used for small circumferences</p>
